                p.is-size-6 Almost every project starts as an excuse to learn something new or practice something I've learned. I develop apps, libraries, and hardware to solve specific problems and enhance my workflow.
                br
                p I've written a few extensions for the Aseprite pixel art editor, all of which are available on my itch.io page for free / "pay what you want"; if you find any of them useful, please consider donating to support future development!
                br
                p My hardware projects include custom mechanical keyboards, guitar effects pedals, and more.
